The paper presents a framework for visual modelling and analysis of complex systems using graph rewriting rules and a user-defined strategy. This involves software engineering (cs.SE) aspects such as tool implementation, programming language (cs.PL) aspects such as operational semantics, logical reasoning (cs.LO) aspects such as graph traversal, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) aspects such as simulation, and systems and control (cs.SY) aspects such as system representation.
